Sentencas: To explore plausible applications of 10 mol% Dy-doped La2Mo2O9 (LDM), we have prepared membrane-electrode assemblies (MEAs) based on this oxide ion conductor and operated them under single chamber conditions of methane and air.
Titulo: Properties of 10% Dy-doped La2Mo2O9 and its electrolyte performance in single chamber solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Material selection is centered on matching thermal expansion of the LDM electrolyte, joined with an anode support of nickel and ceria cermet and a graded cathode of samarium strontium cobaltite plus ceria.
Titulo: Properties of 10% Dy-doped La2Mo2O9 and its electrolyte performance in single chamber solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The performance test results indicate that both open circuit voltage and ohmic loss increase with increasing LDM thickness, leading an optimal LDM thickness 60 mu m.
Titulo: Properties of 10% Dy-doped La2Mo2O9 and its electrolyte performance in single chamber solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: This MEA of 60 mu m thick LDM generates peak power 330 mW cm(-2) at 700 degrees C, which can be upgraded to 420 mW cm(-2) through promoting the anode activity.
Titulo: Properties of 10% Dy-doped La2Mo2O9 and its electrolyte performance in single chamber solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Impedance analysis indicates the electrode improvements are effective, but have limitations, because the major polarization loss resides in the LDM electrolyte.
Titulo: Properties of 10% Dy-doped La2Mo2O9 and its electrolyte performance in single chamber solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: High electrolyte polarization loss originates from two weaknesses of LDM, excessive thermal expansion and vulnerability to hydrogen reduction.
Titulo: Properties of 10% Dy-doped La2Mo2O9 and its electrolyte performance in single chamber solid oxide fuel cell
